1930;;They Learned About Women;;American;;Jack Conway, Sam Wood;;Van and Schenck, Bessie Love;;musical;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/They_Learned_About_Women;;Big-league baseball players Jerry and Jack are also pretty good at singing. They perform in a vaudeville show, where both fall in love with Mary, a dancer, while a second woman tries to come between them before the next World Series.